PATCH: Refined transaction report generation
and updated email links
This update makes the calculation for loss and overall profit in transaction reports more accurate. The false-positive check for loss value has been removed and an overdueAmount now includes 'DISPUTED' payments as well. Further, corrected the redirect URL for the "Go to the dashboard" button in the shop report email to correctly route to the platform shop reports.

BREAKING CHANGES: Add CurrentReports model and ShopReportReady mail class
This commit introduces two new classes - CurrentReports Model and ShopReportReady Mail class. The CurrentReports Model will handle the interaction with the 'current_reports' database table. The ShopReportReady Mail class is responsible for setting up and sending the shop reports once they are ready, including the management of file attachments.
